--no-experiments-async-web-assembly     Negative
                                        'experiments-async-web-assembly'
                                        option.
--experiments-back-compat               Enable backward-compat layer with
                                        deprecation warnings for many webpack
                                        4 APIs.
--no-experiments-back-compat            Negative 'experiments-back-compat'
                                        option.
--experiments-build-http-allowed-uris <value...>  Allowed URI pattern. Allowed URI
                                        (resp. the beginning of it).
--experiments-build-http-allowed-uris-reset  Clear all items provided in
                                        'experiments.buildHttp.allowedUris'
                                        configuration. List of allowed URIs
                                        (resp. the beginning of them).
--experiments-build-http-cache-location <value>  Location where resource content is
                                        stored for lockfile entries. It's also
                                        possible to disable storing by passing
                                        false.
--no-experiments-build-http-cache-location  Negative
                                        'experiments-build-http-cache-location
                                        ' option.
--experiments-build-http-frozen         When set, anything that would lead to
                                        a modification of the lockfile or any
                                        resource content, will result in an
